end  Alice Liddell , daughter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Alice Eginton was born in 1510, in Surrey, England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 daughter with Edward Best. She died in 1547, in her hometown, at the age of 37."},"et":{"1510–1547":"1510–1547","1505–1561":"1505–1561","1528–1572":"1528–1572","1547":"1547","1510":"1510","1572":"1572","1561":"1561","1528":"1528","1505":"1505","Surrey,  England":"Surrey, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Surrey County, England":"Surrey, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Tattenhoe, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom":"Tattenhoe, Buckinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1510–1547":"1510–1547","1505–1561":"1505–1561","1528–1572":"1528–1572","1547":"1547","1510":"1510","1572":"1572","1561":"1561","1528":"1528","1505":"1505","Surrey,  England":"Surrey, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Surrey County, England":"Surrey, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Tattenhoe, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom":"Tattenhoe, Buckinghamshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1510–1547":"1510–1547","1505–1561":"1505–1561","1528–1572":"1528–1572","1547":"1547","1510":"1510","1572":"1572","1561":"1561","1528":"1528","1505":"1505","Surrey,  England":"Surrey, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Surrey County, England":"Surrey, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Tattenhoe, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom":"Tattenhoe, Buckinghamshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Alice Eginton est née en 1510, à Surrey, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Edward Best. Elle est décédée en 1547, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 37 ans."},"de":{"1510–1547":"1510–1547","1505–1561":"1505–1561","1528–1572":"1528–1572","1547":"1547","1510":"1510","1572":"1572","1561":"1561","1528":"1528","1505":"1505","Surrey,  England":"Surrey, England, United Kingdom","Surrey Count